      <title>芯片工人可能辞职，劳动力短缺加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/chip-workers-are-likely-to-quit-jobs-worsening-labor-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦肯锡咨询公司表示，在美国寻求吸引更多技术工人从事半导体制造之际，许多现有员工正在重新考虑是否要留下来。公司报告强调了芯片行业的劳动力挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/chip-workers-are-likely-to-quit-jobs-worsening-labor-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
